    <item>
      <title>&#39;Samba in Seoul&#39; by Jair Martins De Miranda</title>
      <link>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/%EC%9D%8C%EC%95%85/samba-in-seoul-by-jair-martins-de-miranda/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 22:34:15 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/%EC%9D%8C%EC%95%85/samba-in-seoul-by-jair-martins-de-miranda/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;상파울루 주립대학의 인류학 교수 Jair Martins De Miranda 가 2014년 즈음 한국의 브라질리언 뮤지션들을 촬영한 다큐이다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe width=&#34;560&#34; height=&#34;315&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/DsbguUjyWfY&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;그 당시 활동하던 거의 모든 브라질리언 뮤지션들을 촬영했고 인터뷰 했다&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;이 작업은 다큐 삼비스타 Sambistas 의 모티브가 되었다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>다큐멘터리 Sambistas 삼비스타</title>
      <link>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/%EC%9D%8C%EC%95%85/%EB%8B%A4%ED%81%90sambistas/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 22:16:37 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/%EC%9D%8C%EC%95%85/%EB%8B%A4%ED%81%90sambistas/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;판데믹 이전 시대의 낭만. 우리는 돌아갈 수 있을까?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://filmfreeway.com/SAMBISTAS&#34;&gt;https://filmfreeway.com/SAMBISTAS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe width=&#34;560&#34; height=&#34;315&#34; src=&#34;http://storage.googleapis.com/ff-storage-p01/press_kits/trailers/001/394/522/original/31892683-_.mp4?GoogleAccessId=GOOG2M4PJ64TEC4POW5U&amp;Signature=mhaZIr08NI56VMjiLGMEGf3r4Pc%3D&amp;Expires=1587305413&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&#34; allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;바치뉴는 본인이 삼비스타라고 불리는 것을 싫어했다. 하지만 삼비스타라는 제목은 한국의 &amp;lsquo;미래&amp;rsquo; 삼비스타들에게 대한 헌정이라는 의미다.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Last May, 100,000 South Americans at a BTS(K-pop superstar group)&amp;rsquo;s concert in Sao Paulo passionately sang along to the songs in Korean. In opposite parts of the world though the number is smaller, there are musicians in Korea who share a passion for Brazilian music and sing in Portugese. Now begins the story of these Korean Brazilian musicians.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>삼바와 영화를 사랑하는 분들에게 추천하는 브라질의 극영화</title>
      <link>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/movie/%EC%82%BC%EB%B0%94%EC%99%80-%EC%98%81%ED%99%94%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B6%84%EB%93%A4%EC%97%90%EA%B2%8C-%EC%B6%94%EC%B2%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%98%81%ED%99%94/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2019 10:14:03 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bluedskim.github.io/posts/movie/%EC%82%BC%EB%B0%94%EC%99%80-%EC%98%81%ED%99%94%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B6%84%EB%93%A4%EC%97%90%EA%B2%8C-%EC%B6%94%EC%B2%9C%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%98%81%ED%99%94/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;삼바음악을 주요 소재로 하였거나 삼바의 정서saudade가 많이 묻어나는 브라질의 극영화들이다&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Orfeu Negro(흑인 오르페) : &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=642&#34;&gt;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=642&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010182_%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010182_%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;흑인 오르페&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cidade De Deus(시티 오브 갓) : &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=7832&#34;&gt;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=7832&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010003_cityofgod_main_p1%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010003_cityofgod_main_p1%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;시티 오브 갓&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Central Do Brazil(중앙역) : &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=1798&#34;&gt;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=1798&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010001_lposter000476%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://bluedskim.github.io/images/M0010001_lposter000476%5BX230,330%5D.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;중앙역&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;기타&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Woman On Top(맛을 보여드립니다) &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=6472&#34;&gt;http://www.cine21.com/movie/info/?movie_id=6472&lt;/a&gt; : 삼바(보사노바) 음악이 많이 삽입되었지만&#xA;장식적 요소일 뿐 딱히 삼바의 정서가 묻어나지는 않는 영화지만 노래들은 좋다.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
